PortfolioApi -r-> UserApi : calls

database "CosmosDB" {
    entity "[Portfolio Collection]" as PortfolioData
    entity "[User Collection]" as UserData
}


PortfolioApi --> PortfolioData : reads/writes
UserApi --> UserData : reads/writes
@enduml